<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The current docblock for Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::fetchRow() contains:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
* Fetches one row in an object of type Zend_Db_Table_Row_Abstract,
* or returns Boolean false if no row matches the specified criteria.
</code></pre>

<p>However, fetchRow() was previously changed to return NULL, not false, if no row matches the criteria.  The @return parameter correctly states this.</p>

